Dear Advisory Board members,

Please find attached a draft version of the CECs recommendations to council, which were discussed and prepared during the second Electricity Advisory Board meeting November 29th at the Institute of the Americas in La Jolla, California. 

Your comments and feedback would be greatly appreciated, please send comments to Yolanda Clegg (yolanda@ccemtl.org) by January 15th. We will also be contacting you in the New Year should you wish to further discuss the recommendations or prepare additional text/paragraphs for the document. 

